//-Can conatin letters,numbers and underscores.
//-Must  begin with a letter to underscore(_).
//-Cannot begin with numbers.
//-Cannot use C++ reserved keywords.
//-C+++ is case sensitive.
//-Cannot redclare a name in the same scope.

